PV panel controller project

PINS AND PERIPHERIALS USED:

GPIOA:
PA0     ------> ADC1
PA1     ------> ADC2
PA4     ------> ADC3
PB0     ------> ADC4

SERVO:
PC6     ------> SERVO 1 PWM (TIM3_CH1) HORIZONTAL
PC8     ------> SERVO 2 PWM (TIM3_CH3) VERTICAL

USART(FOR HC-05 COMMUNICATION):
PA9     ------> USART TX
PA10     ------> USART RX

I2C1(FOR LCD COMMUNICATION):
PB6     ------> USART TX
PB7     ------> USART RX